  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the roll of pre-operative chest physiotherapy, in
      addition to the usual care given after major abdominal surgery, in the prevention of
      post-operative respiratory complications.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
